98-3074 (La. 4/1/99)

STATE ex rel. Robert LIDDELL v. STATE of Louisiana. No. 98-KH-3074. Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 1, 1999.

IN RE: Liddell, Robert; — Plaintiff(s); Applying for Supervisory and/or Remedial Writ; Parish of Jefferson 24th Judicial District Court Div. “I” Number 95-4480; to the Court of Appeal, Fifth Circuit, Number 98-KH-1011

Denied. La.C.Cr.P. art. 930.3; State ex rel. Melinie v. State, 93-1380 (La.1/12/96), 665 So.2d 1172.

JOHNSON, J. not on panel.
